com.brashmonkey.spriter

Class Point

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.brashmonkey.spriter.Point
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    IKObject

    public class Point
extends java.lang.Object
    A utility class to keep the code short. A point is essentially that what you would expect if you think about a point in a 2D space. It holds an x and y value. You can translate(Point), scale(Point), rotate(float) and set(Point) a point.
